text: Erwin Carl Gangl is an electrical engineer who works for CACI, Inc. in Centerville, OH. He was named Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2013 for his development of digital avionics intra-communication systems and Mil-Std-1553. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
